      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, if im already shaky, wont taking the insulin make the hypoglycemia even worse? like, if i take it now and my sugar is already trending down, im gonna crash for real. i just want a simple answer, is skipping it really more dangerous than a low? i just dont want to end up in the ER.",
